{
  "texts": [
    "Results of this search and screening are summarised in Fig. 2.",
    "Research outputsTo complement our search of REC applications, we conducted a bibliographic search of the Web of Science (WoS) core collection (Fig. 3), which provides comparable coverage to Scopus as an indexed article collection [12,77].",
    "This approach was intended to (1) act as a check on further applications that may have been missed in the internalsystem search; and (2) provide further insight regarding the expression of ethics by researchers, through analysis of reflections of ethics in their published works.",
    "8 We also conducted a search for obtained REC numbers (e.g.",
    "searching for \"REC-15000\") in Google Scholar, to supplement the materials in the REC process, though this did not identify any further material."
  ]
}